<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zie khawvela ka lenlai hin,
 Ni chengin buoina'n ei bawm;
 Thihna lui Jordan ka kaih ma chun,
 Lalpa lungkhamna a khawk diek ie.

[V2]
 Ei thilsak inla, Na siem Salem,
 Lungtuok Angel lai lenna khen lohna gam chu,
 Khawvel lung khamna pawtsan in,
 Aw bangtik leh ka hung tung deimawh?

[V3]
 2. Ma a lungngai a maute khan,
 Mun lopi chu a tun un;
 Chieh masa leh Angel vamte tawh,
 Aw Salem Lalpa a chawian ui.

[V4]
 3. A kumsawt lau sakpih dingin,
 Aw ei sam hehpih chieh te'n;
 A gihawih u leh thawm ka zakin,
 Aw, ziemun lopi ngai chun kakap.

[V5]
 4. Ka ngai na e Immanuel,
 Na siem Salem thak nuom chu;
 Ka lenna gamthip ahi Lalpa,
 Tun loh kalau ie ei hung puiin.</lyrics>
<title>Na Siem Salem Thak !</title>
<hymn_number>180</hymn_number>
</song>